<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-21 10:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2695 &Cx1f; tib-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBA-ANDERSON-COLUMN-N     11-21 0766
