   ROGER-CLINTON _ President Clinton and his half-brother Roger
share a moment in Korea on his Asian tour as rock show Seoul-mates
. (Deans, Cox News Service) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA-WINTER _ PETROPAVLOVSK-KAMCHATSKY, Russia _ Outside their
apartments, temperatures are well below freezing. Inside their
apartments, the mercury isn't much higher. Russia's economic crisis
and the onset of the country's brutal winter are a dangerous
combination in this Pacific port city. Fuel shortages have cut heat
and electricity to thousands of homes and caused several deaths.
Food shortages also are expected in this forsaken part of Russia
seven times zones east of Moscow. (Holmes, Cox News Service). MOVED
</P>
