<P>
   CHINA-ELECTIONS _ HUNAN PROVINCE, China _ A color story on
Chinese villagers exercising a rare bit of democracy in China, the
right to choose their lowest level local leaders. In China, only
village dwellers have this right, but experts from the
Atlanta-based Carter Center are here with computers and technical
assistance to help the Chinese make the experiment work.
(Kunstel/Albright, Cox News Service). MOVED FRIDAY. WITH PHOTO
</P>
