<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Saturday, 11/21/98. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   NIGERIA/Ojobo Locator -- 1X2 1/4 -- NIGERIA-REBELS
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO/San Cristobal Locator -- 1X2 3/4 -- MEXICO-REBELS
</P>
<P>
   TV/Age Groups Targeted -- 2X8 3/4 -- TV-NETWORK-SLUMP
</P>
<P>
   TV/Network Ratings Slump -- 1X2 3/8 -- TV-NETWORK-SLUMP
</P>
<P>
   SAFETY-LIGHTS/Vehicles, Vision.pdf -- 2X5 7/8 --
SAFETY-LIGHTS-TRUCK
</P>
