</P>
<P>
   ``How useful will they be? Who knows! It depends on your
situation when you cash it out.'' &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL; 
</P>
<ANNOTATION>
    &UR; (STORY CAN END HERE AT 550. OPTIONAL MATERIAL FOLLOWS) &LR;  &QC; 
</ANNOTATION>
 &LR;  &QL;
<P>
   Here are five scenarios that might help to make sense out of
